description:
Evil has cleared the Eastern Seaboard of human life and now is turning his attention inland. Meanwhile Dr Price and Dr Young are now charged with putting a stop to the undead maniac. They explore the very beginnings of Ernie's undead rampage and come up with a plan to take him down and sever him from the power that keeps him going once and for all. Smiley button's personality starts to come to the front as he advises Ernie on tactics and the special relationship between them is explored. Meanwhile in Hell Lady Death is tormented by visions and is unable to control her own kingdom as a winged tormentor haunted her every move.

Collected in Evil Ernie: Revenge.

description:
Lady Death has reigned in Hell for 400 years when an unseen attacker torments her dreams and twists her realm while she is  awake. He foe is the demonic Purgatori and she has a thrist for the blood of gods and immortals. She is a master deceiver and it take all lady Death's cunning to bring out her foe so that they might battle face to face. But things are not as they seem and the pair are in fact puppets of a greater deceiver. Old friends and and enemies clash in this new epic tale. 
 
This series runs directly into Chaos Quarterly 1 story arc and is preceded by the original series The Reckoning .

description:
The Elephantmen series follows the on going battles of the giant mutated animal/human crossbreed creatures created by a shadowy organisation as war machines that do battle in Africa, killing without mercy.

Years later these same creatures are rehabilitated as members of society, some still working for covert organisations, and haunted by the shame of their actions and the nature of their birth. We follow the story of Hip Flask and Ebony Hide (Hippopotamus and Elephant crosses respectively) as they try to get by in a world in which they are shunned and treated with suspicion.

description:
Ernie is trapped.... trapped in the mind of Stone after his physical body was destroyed. However its not all bad for our psychotic madman, he gets to spend time with his mistress Lady Death. Between them they hatch a plan to get megadeath back on track and Ernie out in the world killing again. Meanwhile the senate is looking for someone to blame for the 200,000 dead and the carnage Ernie caused. In the firing line is Dr Price & Young whose machine they believe gave Ernie his powers. Watch as Ernie once again reeks havoc on earth and this time.. he wont stop until he reaches the Whitehouse.

Collected in Evil Ernie: The Resurrection.
